version_description: In other versions the final verse isnt quite right towards the end, causing the player to lose their way slightly before the final chorus. This version flows better.
Studio recording off the album XO. A recording can be found here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5qhPPnroLQ4.
Chords are more accurate to the original song. Make sure you sing in a whispering voice.

song_name: She Wont Ever Look At Me
